---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Home | Reality Foundation" active="home">
  <section class="panel">
    <h1>RealityCheck</h1>
    <p class="muted">
      RealityCheck is a project to prove that selected photos are real by combining trusted mobile capture,
      integrity checks, cryptographic hashing, and immutable records.
    </p>
    <p>
      The focus is not to detect AI-generated media in general. The focus is to certify specific images with
      verifiable evidence from capture to publication.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
    <h2>Project Snapshot</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Trusted app + device integrity verification before capture</li>
      <li>Image and metadata hashing after capture</li>
      <li>Blockchain-backed immutable timestamps for auditability</li>
      <li>Verification-friendly sharing for portals and embeds</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
